      <title>美国抵押贷款利率连续三周下跌后上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-mortgage-rates-rise-after-three-straight-weekly-declines-2024-12-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国抵押贷款利率在连续三周下跌后本周有所上升，美联储预测 2025 年降息次数将减少，从而推高了 10 年期美国国债收益率，之后抵押贷款利率可能进一步上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-mortgage-rates-rise-after-three-straight-weekly-declines-2024-12-19/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 18:14:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
